OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDrink driver blames Covid  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor M4 drive with missing  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftyres                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A drink driver travelled for 10 miles  
OL,6, down the M4 with two tyres missing     
OL,7, after a night out with friends.        
OL,9,FDespite being twice the limit and      
OL,10,Fadmitting drink driving, Laurie Rosser,
OL,11,F42, blamed Covid for making his mind   
OL,12,F"cloudy".                              
OL,14,FSwansea Magistrates' Court heard       
OL,15,FRosser, from Gorseinon, had two wheel  
OL,16,F"blowouts" on his Vauxhall van on 26   
OL,17,FJune, yet continued driving.           
OL,19,FHe was banned from driving for 17      
OL,20,Fmonths and fined #300.                 
